### Get All Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Payment
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Pay Bill
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/bills
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "billerName": "Electric Company",
  "category": "Utilities",
  "accountNumber": "123456789",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "description": "Monthly electric bill"
}

### Pay Utility
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/utilities
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "providerName": "Water Company",
  "utilityType": "Water",
  "meterNumber": "987654321",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "description": "Monthly water bill"
}

### Pay Merchant
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/merchants
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "merchantName": "Supermarket",
  "merchantId": "MERCH123",
  "category": "Groceries",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "description": "Weekly groceries"
}

### Schedule Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/scheduled
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "paymentType": "BILL",
  "category": "Utilities",
  "payeeName": "Electric Company",
  "payeeAccount": "123456789",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "scheduledDate": "2023-12-31",
  "description": "Scheduled electric bill"
}

### Get Scheduled Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/scheduled?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Create Recurring Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/recurring
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "paymentType": "BILL",
  "category": "Utilities",
  "payeeName": "Electric Company",
  "payeeAccount": "123456789",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "frequency": "MONTHLY",
  "startDate": "2023-01-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-31",
  "description": "Monthly electric bill"
}

### Get Recurring Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/recurring?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Recurring Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/recurring/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Save Biller
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/billers
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "billerName": "Electric Company",
  "category": "Utilities",
  "accountNumber": "123456789",
  "nickname": "My Electric Bill"
}

### Get Saved Billers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/billers?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Delete Biller
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/billers/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Payment Receipt
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/1/receipt
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Pending Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/pending?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Payment Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/statistics
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Payment Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/categories
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/health
